EASTERN MEDITERRANEAN.
LIBYA.
NGA CHART 56220 (4TH ED).
1. APPROACHES TO MISURATA (32-22N 015-05E)
   DANGEROUS TO SHIPPING.
2. INBOUND VESSELS STRONGLY ADVISED TO REMAIN
   CLEAR OF AREA BOUND BY
   32-26N 015-00E, 32-31N 015-00E,
   32-31N 015-30E, 32-20N 015-30E,
   32-20N 015-16E.
3. CONTACT HQ MC NAPLES FOR UPDATES ON THE
   SITUATION, PHONE: 00 800 110 1010,
   E-MAIL: MOCN3DOGCELL@MANP.NATO.INT.
4. OUTBOUND VESSELS FROM MISURATA HARBORS
   RECOMMENDED TO CLOSELY LIAISE WITH LOCAL
   PORT AUTHORITIES FOR ADVICE.
